&lt;p&gt;Practice Development Nurse – Surgery&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;‘How high can you fly on your journey in Professional &amp; Practice Development?’&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Come and join us as we move forward with our professionally led nursing &amp; midwifery strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our strategy, written and delivered by our nursing &amp; midwifery team includes; leadership, professional development, well-being and staff recognition as part of our journey to Pathway to Excellence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can offer you an exciting opportunity to influence and support our registrants to deliver excellence evidence based patient care in a working environment that believes in you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be part of an established, experienced Professional Practice Development Team that can support you to grow professionally. This is a unique opportunity to grow with your ideas in a supportive and constructive setting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can offer you personal professional development, academic support, clinical supervision and one to one coaching to enhance and upskill your knowledge and competence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
